(Translated by Google) About 15 minutes walk from Ala Moana Center. I want to eat curry and come to the store.  The specialty crab curry is the market price. Half day size $30. The amount of crab in it is amazing, but the shells are cooked, so you can eat it from your fingertips to your wrists. The taste is outstanding.  The dessert mango pudding has a richer taste than the mango pulp itself. I want you to eat it because you think you were tricked.
